        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks GHKT for specimens of <hi rend="italic">Sethia</hi>. Discusses functions of their dimorphism for insect fertilisation.</p> 
            <p>Discusses polymorphism and fertilisation in Lythraceae.</p> 
<p>Asks for seed of <hi rend="italic">Limnanthemum</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Describes his interest in galls.</p> 
<p>Discusses curious specimens of <hi rend="italic">Gomphia</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Lesemia</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
